{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"stroke-dashoffset","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-dashoffset","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG</a>属性参考主页</p>\n\n<p><code>stroke-dashoffset</code> 属性指定了 dash 模式到路径开始的距离</p>\n\n<p>如果使用了一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#percentage\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Percentage\">&lt;百分比&gt;</a>&nbsp;值， 那么这个值就代表了当前 viewport 的一个百分比。<br>\n <br>\n 值可以取为负值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用环境","title":"使用环境","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>显示属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#percentage\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Percentage\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a> | <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#length\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Length\">&lt;length&gt;</a> | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">初始值</th>\n   <td>1</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可动画</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#StrokeDashoffsetProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可使用 stroke-dashoffset 属性</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#shape\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Shape\">形状元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#textcontent\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#TextContent\">文本内容元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用环境","id":"使用环境"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG属性参考主页","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"20